Copy this file to .env and fill in the values.

Set this to the absolute path of a Git repository on your local machine for testing.

Example for Windows: LOCAL_REPO_PATH=C:\Users\YourName\projects\my-test-repo

Example for Linux/macOS: LOCAL_REPO_PATH=/home/yourname/projects/my-test-repo

LOCAL_REPO_PATH=

